  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Space Combat Simulator!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/7c5562b01ca40c0339d640942b7fefcd.avif?t=1772360408\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pilot your starship in Starship Fighters, a realistic space combat simulator. Engage in intense battles, explore vast galaxies, and unleash destruction with an arsenal of powerful weapons in a universe teeming with enemies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.poster.avif?t=1772360408\" width=602 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.webm?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.mp4?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Starship Fighters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starship Fighters immerses players in thrilling space combat across the vast universe. As a starship pilot, embark on intense missions that test your combat skills and strategy. Customize a variety of starships, each equipped with powerful weapons for scenarios ranging from dogfights to large-scale battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.poster.avif?t=1772360408\" width=604 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.webm?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.mp4?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a detailed galaxy with diverse environments, from asteroid fields to alien planets, each offering unique tactical challenges. Engage in high-speed chases, outmaneuver enemies, and unleash powerful attacks to dominate the cosmos. With immersive 3D visuals and first-person action, Starship Fighters offers modes for endless replayability, delivering intense, adrenaline-fueled action in every battle.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pilot your starship in Starship Fighters, a realistic space combat simulator. Engage in intense battles, explore vast galaxies, and unleash destruction with an arsenal of powerful weapons in a universe teeming with enemies!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.poster.avif?t=1772360408\" width=602 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.webm?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/34096036364cb288db26af8b86e412a3.mp4?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Starship Fighters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Starship Fighters immerses players in thrilling space combat across the vast universe. As a starship pilot, embark on intense missions that test your combat skills and strategy. Customize a variety of starships, each equipped with powerful weapons for scenarios ranging from dogfights to large-scale battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.poster.avif?t=1772360408\" width=604 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.webm?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213000/extras/d7236f5c5abbdc3549cd2c6882fca8c3.mp4?t=1772360408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a detailed galaxy with diverse environments, from asteroid fields to alien planets, each offering unique tactical challenges. Engage in high-speed chases, outmaneuver enemies, and unleash powerful attacks to dominate the cosmos. With immersive 3D visuals and first-person action, Starship Fighters offers modes for endless replayability, delivering intense, adrenaline-fueled action in every battle.</p>",
